HEADWORD: mammothrept
<hw>mam"mo*thrept</hw> <pr>(m⟦acr⟧m"m⟦osl⟧*thr⟦ecr⟧pt)</pr>,
<pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <grk>mammo`qreptos</grk>; <grk>ma`mma</grk>
